The paper focuses on software architecture and design decisions, which are key topics in software engineering (cs.SE). It also involves analyzing code and identifying patterns, which falls under programming languages (cs.PL) and software development (cs.SD). The paper also discusses the preservation and evolution of architectural decisions, which could be relevant to machine learning (cs.LG) and cybersecurity (cs.CY) as these fields often involve maintaining and updating complex systems.
